{
  "stem": "4113.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Used to tell us how fine they were.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You see.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Anyway, at the end of 1943 the order came that the entire command of the Luftwaffe in our town-- you see, this was a [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That was-- it was a school for-- a technical school for flyers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "No, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Four.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was under the command of Breslau.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Anyway, the entire command-- the whole [GERMAN]-- is to go to the east.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because now they were having to fight in the east.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And, of course, they had Stalingrad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Now they had the big battles at Kursk, you know, at Kirvoy Rog.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they had to go to the east.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course, they're all young kids at the airbase.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And a command from the east-- tired soldiers are going to come and take over the airbase.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now we got scared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What's going to happen to us?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So Mr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Langsome went to talk to the-- to the people in charge at the airbase.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they promised that they will do their best to keep us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They will talk to the command that's going to take over.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, introduce us to them and ask them that they should try to keep us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because the SS always wanted us back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, to give you the extent of their cooperation with us, that when the SS came from Krakow-Plaszow to visit-- to see what goes on-- they had the order to hold them at the gate.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they let us know that they're there, and we took the pictures up from our barracks and threw everything aside so that they won't see it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because one time-- the first time they came-- was-- was a Untersturmfuhrer [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Jan ?] from Krakow-Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He came to inspect.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
